rows.label: qst202502_0010
rows.name:
Enemy reinforcements confirmed. Requesting
permission to continue combat...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202502_0020
rows.name: No, it's no use. This is endless.

rows.label: qst202502_0030
rows.name:
KOS-MOS Re:, let's fall back
and rethink our strategy.

rows.label: qst202502_0040
rows.name:
If we retreat under the current circumstances,
there is a risk of damage to various locations.

rows.label: qst202502_0050
rows.name:
It is judged that we should continue
to annihilate the enemy entities...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202502_0060
rows.name:
That's what you say, but there
are so many, it's difficult.

rows.label: qst202502_0070
rows.name:
Yeah. One wrong move and we'll be
the ones getting annihilated.

rows.label: qst202502_0080
rows.name:
There is no problem. Everyone,
please move away from me.

rows.label: qst202502_0100
rows.name:
Lock-on complete for all enemy entities
deployed around the World Tree.

rows.label: qst202502_0150
rows.name:
Commencing mop-up of
remaining enemy forces.

rows.label: qst202502_0180
rows.name:
Uh, ah...[ML:Dash ] No. Right, let's
take out the rest of them.
